ner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"1867\" data-end=\"2032\">Acacia wood is a durable hardwood with rich natural grain patterns.<br data-start=\"1934\" data-end=\"1937\" \/>It is widely used for <strong data-start=\"1959\" data-end=\"2031\">wooden plates, serving trays, cutting boards, and kitchen organizers<\/strong>.<\/p><p data-start=\"2034\" data-end=\"2053\"><strong data-start=\"2034\" data-end=\"2053\">Key advantages:<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"2054\" data-end=\"2198\"><li data-start=\"2054\" data-end=\"2086\"><p data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2086\">Strong and durable structure<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2087\" data-end=\"2137\"><p data-start=\"2089\" data-end=\"2137\">Natural color variation for premium appearance<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2138\" data-end=\"2198\"><p data-start=\"2140\" data-end=\"2198\">Suitable for food-contact products with proper finishing<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2200\" data-end=\"2292\">Acacia wood is one of the most popular choices for mid-range to premium kitchenware markets.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ea90a8 e-con-full e-flex elementor-repeater-item-default_padding elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2ea90a8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ang_container_spacing_size&quot;:&quot;default_padding&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-745b8fe external_elementor-repeater-item-none_external elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"745b8fe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/S1c2480d5412745428726c9f1dbc18ba