umers.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-105e1db elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"105e1db\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"2313\" data-end=\"2425\">Bamboo is an eco-friendly and fast-growing material commonly used in <strong data-start=\"2382\" data-end=\"2424\">kitchen storage, trays, and organizers<\/strong>.<\/p><p data-start=\"2427\" data-end=\"2446\"><strong data-start=\"2427\" data-end=\"2446\">Key advantages:<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"2447\" data-end=\"2570\"><li data-start=\"2447\" data-end=\"2491\"><p data-start=\"2449\" data-end=\"2491\">Sustainable and environmentally friendly<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2492\" data-end=\"2531\"><p data-start=\"2494\" data-end=\"2531\">Stable structure and smooth surface<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2532\" data-end=\"2570\"><p data-start=\"2534\" data-end=\"2570\">Cost-effective for mass production<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2572\" data-end=\"2650\">Bamboo products are especially popular in European and North American markets.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e6e68d9 e-con-full e-flex elementor-repeater-item-default_padding elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e6e68d9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ang_container_spacing_size&quot;:&quot;default_padding&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1a2f72 external_elementor-repeater-item-none_external elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e1a2f72\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div cl