ement elementor-element-3ddf9f6 elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3ddf9f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>MDF is often used as a budget-friendly alternative among wood materials for kitchenware.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aff2d1e elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"aff2d1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"5245\" data-end=\"5346\">MDF is an engineered wood material widely used in <strong data-start=\"5295\" data-end=\"5345\">budget-oriented storage and organizer products<\/strong>.<\/p><p data-start=\"5348\" data-end=\"5367\"><strong data-start=\"5348\" data-end=\"5367\">Key advantages:<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"5368\" data-end=\"5460\"><li data-start=\"5368\" data-end=\"5413\"><p data-start=\"5370\" data-end=\"5413\">Smooth surface for painting or laminating<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5414\" data-end=\"5436\"><p data-start=\"5416\" data-end=\"5436\">Consistent quality<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5437\" data-end=\"5460\"><p data-start=\"5439\" data-end=\"5460\">Lower material cost<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"5462\" data-end=\"5536\">MDF allows flexible designs and decorative finishes at competitive prices.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c30dce e-con-full elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover e-flex elementor-repeater-item-default_padding e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4c30dce\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ang_container_spacing_size&quot;:&quot;d