commerce-loop-product__title\">Hand-Carved Leaf Shaped Acacia Wood Serving Tray &#038; Decorative Platter<\/h2><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/product\/wholesale-leaf-shaped-wood-tray-hand-carved-acacia-serving-platter\/\" aria-describedby=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_3161\" data-quantity=\"1\" class=\"button product_type_variable\" data-product_id=\"3161\" data-product_sku=\"CJJJCFCJ01148\" aria-label=\"Select options for &ldquo;Hand-Carved Leaf Shaped Acacia Wood Serving Tray &amp; Decorative Platter&rdquo;\" rel=\"nofollow\">Read more<\/a>\t<span id=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_3161\" class=\"screen-reader-text\">\n\t\t\t<\/span>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-79e8d25 e-flex e-con-boxed elementor-repeater-item-default_padding elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"79e8d25\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ang_container_spacing_size&quot;:&quot;default_padding&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a66482a elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a66482a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 data-path-to-node=\"5\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">1. Why Choose Our Wholesale Wooden Serving Trays?<\/b><\/h4><p data-path-to-node=\"6\">In the world of home decor and hospitality, plastic is out, and nature is in. <b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">Wooden Serving Trays<\/b> are no longer just functional items for carrying drinks; they are essential decor elements for coffee tables, ottomans, and kitchen islands. For retailers and F&amp;B brands, stocking high-quality wooden platters offers a high-margin product that appeals to eco-conscious consumers.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\">As a premier <b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"13\">Wooden Serving Tray Manufacturer in China<\/b>, Xiamen Chic Homeware helps you capitalize on this trend. We don&#8217;t just cut wood; we engineer durable, food-safe, and aesthetically stunning serving solutions tailored for the global market.<\/p><h4 data-path-to-node=\"8\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">2. Material Guide: Acacia vs. Bamboo vs. Walnut<\/b><\/h4><p data-path-to-node=\"9\">Choosing the right wood is crucial for your target market. Here is a breakdown of the materials we offer:<\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"10\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Acacia Wood (Best Seller):<\/b> Known for its high density and distinctive grain patterns. It ranges from rich dark browns to golden honey tones. It is naturally water-resistant and antimicrobial, making it the top choice for <b data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"221\">Cheese Boards<\/b> and <b data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"239\">Charcuterie Platters<\/b>.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bamboo (Eco-Friendly):<\/b> Technically a grass, bamboo is harder than maple and incredibly sustainable. It offers a uniform, clean blonde look. Our <b data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"144\">Bamboo Serving Trays<\/b> are lightweight, affordable, and perfect for high-volume retail or promotional gift sets.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Rubberwood &amp; Pine:<\/b> Excellent budget-friendly options. While softer, they are perfect for painted finishes or rustic &#8220;farmhouse&#8221; style trays where a distressed look is desired.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h4 data-path-to-node=\"11\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">3. Factory Insights: How We Ensure Quality<\/b><\/h4><p data-path-to-node=\"12\">Importing wooden products can be risky if the manufacturer doesn&#8217;t understand wood science. Here is how we prevent common issues like warping and cracking:<\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"13\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Moisture Content Control:<\/b> We strictly dry our lumber to 8-12% moisture content before production. This ensures the tray stays flat even when shipped from humid China to dry climates like Arizona or Northern Europe.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Food-Safe Finishes:<\/b> Safety is non-negotiable. All our serving trays are finished with FDA and LFGB-compliant oils, waxes, or varnishes. Whether it&#8217;s a matte oil finish for a natural feel or a high-gloss lacquer for easy cleaning, we ensure it&#8217;s safe for direct food contact.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"13,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"13,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Precision Sanding:<\/b> A rough tray feels cheap. We employ a multi-step sanding process, finishing with fine-grit sandpaper to ensure every handle, corner, and surface is silky smooth to the touch.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h4 data-path-to-node=\"14\"><b data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">4. Versatile Designs for Every Occasion<\/b><\/h4><p data-path-to-node=\"15\">Our catalog features diverse structures to meet different buyer needs:<\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"16\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"16,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"16,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">The Ottoman Tray:<\/b> Large, rectangular trays with high sides and sturdy cutout handles. Built to hold heavy coffee pots or serve breakfast in bed.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">The Party Platter:<\/b> Featuring our innovative <b data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"44\">Divided Bamboo Trays with Clear Lids<\/b>. These are game-changers for outdoor catering, picnics, or keeping snacks fresh and pest-free.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"16,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"16,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Seasonal Shapes:<\/b> From Christmas tree-shaped dishes to heart-shaped Valentine&#8217;s platters, we have the molds ready to boost your Q4 sales.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h4 data-path-to-node=\"17\"><b data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">5. Customization &amp; OEM Services<\/b><\/h4><p data-path-to-node=\"18\">Stand out from the competition with our branding options:<\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"19\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Laser Engraving:<\/b> Burn your logo into the tray center or handle for a permanent brand mark.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Custom Color:<\/b> We can stain wood to match &#8220;Walnut,&#8221; &#8220;Cherry,&#8221; or &#8220;Black Oak&#8221; tones to fit your collection&#8217;s color palette.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"19,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Retail Packaging:<\/b> We design color sleeves, gift boxes, or PDQ displays to maximize shelf appeal.<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-81b54c9 e-flex e-con-boxed elementor-repeater-item-default_padding elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-item-none_hover e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"81b54c9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ang_container_spacing_size&quot;:&quot;default_padding&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-169c4ab elementor-repeater-item-none elementor-repeater-it